308
00:19:04,010 --> 00:19:04,740
Impossible.

309
00:19:05,850 --> 00:19:07,550
The center of the formation must be in the city.

310
00:19:07,550 --> 00:19:09,080
But we haven't found it yet.

311
00:19:09,110 --> 00:19:09,920
How about this?

312
00:19:09,920 --> 00:19:11,080
Let's split up to look for it later.

313
00:19:11,080 --> 00:19:13,590
I'll go to the south of the city, while you'll go to the north.

314
00:19:13,590 --> 00:19:14,570
