00:32:20,440 --> 00:32:21,150
No!

526
00:32:21,310 --> 00:32:22,930
Yun Xi, no!

527
00:32:23,700 --> 00:32:24,620
Help me!

528
00:32:24,730 --> 00:32:26,140
Yun Xi, help me!

529
00:32:26,230 --> 00:32:27,860
Help me! No!

530
00:32:28,170 --> 00:32:29,070
Help me!

531
00:32:29,180 --> 00:32:30,300
